.pHive/*
# Legacy state/ — ignored completely. Harness sessions running the pre-rename
# Stop hook may briefly recreate state/interrupts/ files until the session
# restarts. Keeping state/ ignored prevents those files from polluting PRs.
state/
# meta-team state, team configs, and team-memories are plugin-level and should be tracked
!.pHive/meta-team/
!.pHive/meta-team/**
!.pHive/teams/
!.pHive/teams/**
!.pHive/team-memories/
!.pHive/team-memories/**
agents/memories/
.claude/settings.local.json
.history/
.DS_Store
*.log
.claude/*.lock
